# Teaching: Signal Definition — Canonical "patch-now alert" + lifecycle

**Type:** Protocol Correction
**Version:** 1.0.0
**Created:** 2026-04-28
**safe_to_auto_adopt:** true
**Affects:** wai-signal-capture.md, wai-reference.md, spoke_expediter.py
**Supersedes:** nothing
